sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant LB as Load Balancer
    participant A as API Gateway
    participant FA as Flask API
    participant FAPI as FastAPI
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant Q as Queue

    %% Solicitudes de escritura
    C->>LB: POST /api/users
    LB->>A: Routing
    A->>FA: POST /users
    activate FA

    FA->>PG: INSERT users
    activate PG
    PG-->>FA: user_id: 123
    deactivate PG

    FA->>R: Cache user data
    activate R
    R-->>FA: OK
    deactivate R

    FA->>Q: Publish event
    activate Q
    Q-->>FA: ACK
    deactivate Q

    FA-->>A: 201 Created
    deactivate FA
    A-->>LB: 201 Created
    LB-->>C: 201 Created

    Note over C,Q: Escritura concluida

    %% Solicitudes de leitura
    C->>LB: GET /api/users/123
    LB->>A: Routing
    A->>FAPI: GET /users/:id
    activate FAPI

    FAPI->>R: GET cache
    activate R
    R-->>FAPI: user_data
    deactivate R

    alt Cache miss
        FAPI->>PG: SELECT users
        activate PG
        PG-->>FAPI: user_row
        deactivate PG
        FAPI->>R: SET cache
        activate R
        R-->>FAPI: OK
        deactivate R
    end

    FAPI-->>A: 200 OK
    deactivate FAPI
    A-->>LB: 200 OK
    LB-->>C: user_data

    Note over C,FAPI: Leitura concluida